text: Bratsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Ivano-Kazansky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 10 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Iglino, 3 km from Ivano-Kazanka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Bratsky, Republic of Bashkortostan
